{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"delay"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UInt8","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V"},{"kind":"text","text":"?"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The purpose of this field is to synchronize transitions initiated","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"by sending the same message multiple times with a short delay.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"For example, a Node would want to send a Generic On Off Set"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Unacknowledged message to a Group Address. In order to increase"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"changes of successful delivery, such message can be repeated."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The first message could be sent with longer "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage\/delay"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and each following with a shorter one, so when different Nodes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"receive different messages, the action they take seems more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"synchronized."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This file has to be set together with "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage\/transitionTime","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/GenericOnOffSet\/delay"},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/genericonoffset\/delay"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh","doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/GenericOnOffSet"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Message execution delay in 5 millisecond steps."}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"NordicMesh"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"delay"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UInt8"},{"kind":"text","text":"?"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","title":"delay","symbolKind":"property","role":"symbol","externalID":"s:10NordicMesh15GenericOnOffSetV5delays5UInt8VSgvp"},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/TransitionMessage/transitionTime":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage\/transitionTime","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/transitionmessage\/transitiontime","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Transition Time field identifies the time that an Element will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"take to transition to the target state from the present state."}],"required":true,"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"transitionTime"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"TransitionTime","preciseIdentifier":"s:10NordicMesh14TransitionTimeV"},{"kind":"text","text":"?"}],"title":"transitionTime"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh":{"abstract":[{"text":"Provision, configure and control Bluetooth mesh devices with nRF Mesh library.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","title":"NordicMesh","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh"},"doc://NordicMesh/d